Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Waaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pushed out into the world, we are born!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Adjust to your surroundings!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump out, and breathing from the lungs is an emergency must!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, make some music - your very first shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy b-day! The birth of new life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey boy - this world is ruthless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey girl - it's a solitary warground
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A survival game with no start-overs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Beep beep! Cry all you want
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use reaching out desperately
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The rule here is that there's no getting by easy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What about my disturbance-free shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I still want to live snug and cozy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Panic upon realizing there's no going back, ever
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We are simply poor, helpless beings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dropped in a wilderness full of unknown creatures, ego, and ambition...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.37,0:00:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold me, mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We are born now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have always, with tears in our eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,searched for a reason to live in this new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Born now - we have nothing to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have nothing to fear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet powerlessly, ironically, we are born!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A fanfare rises, fever & dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't a disco - it's discommunication!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to tell you, but I no hablo language!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak! Babel will come later - catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The origin of all of humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,(I am a baby. I am a baby. I'm a baby.)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how great they were
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,(Yes, yes, yes, yes. I was, once.)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Life continues on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(Fear & fearless, a neverending cycle.)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,From the moment they awaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Misfortunes seldom come alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No voice - Where we're born...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No choice - Who we'll meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, they're not for us to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting off being a nobody
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"For a cute little baby like you..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Forced to assume an identity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"Baby, let me give you a name!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.11,0:02:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,An unstoppable rollercoaster ride driven by the forces of fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's too late to get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We are born now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We have always, with tears in our eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,been unable to stop ourselves from stepping into a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Born now - we are hurt countless times,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and betrayed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But we will never lose hope
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ironically, as if it were love, we are born!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep within the darkness, we found a light (To the light...)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever drawn to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we've crawled our way out of our comfortable world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Through a dark, narrow path (Onwards, onwards...)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All alone (Onto the next world...)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We are born now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We have always, with tears in our eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,searched for a reason to live in this new world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Born now - we have nothing to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have nothing to fear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Born now! Born now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of securing our rebirth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,cast aside your fear, raise your head, and let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet powerlessly, ironically, we are born!
